---
title: Chinese Ginger Beef Fried Rice with Rainbow Veg
description: Eating the rainbow is easy when you pack it all into a flavourful fried rice. This family favourite uses a clever method – you add the cooked rice to the egg and scramble it all together. It’s a Cantonese-style technique and you’ll quickly understand why – it saves time and spreads the egg evenly through the dish for a perfectly balanced bite!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5b8dca1c30006c6ccd7787c2-90208292.jpg
